title: Prasini Agora
description: Sells a large variety of vegan food products including tofu, cheese, cream, oat/sesame/corn/soya milk, tahini, cereal, grains, nuts, fruits, vegetables and more. Also sells  vitamins, cosmetics, washing powders and others. Located right behind the city court. Address in Greek: Πράσινη Αγορά Γ.Καρτάλη 97
